<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/chevening-foundation> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Chevening Scholarships are the UK government’s global scholarships programme. Established in 1983, these scholarships support study at UK universities - mostly one-year Masters’ degrees - for students with demonstrable potential to become future leaders, decision-makers and opinion formers."@en .
